org.apache.poi.poifs.filesystem

Class POIFSDocument

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.poifs.filesystem.POIFSDocument
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.nio.ByteBuffer>, POIFSViewable

    public final class POIFSDocument
extends java.lang.Object
implements POIFSViewable, java.lang.Iterable<java.nio.ByteBuffer>
    This class manages a document in the NIO POIFS filesystem. This is the POIFSFileSystem version.
